      "created": "2025-08-11T15:11:09.419-0700",
      "updated": "2025-08-11T15:11:09.419-0700",
      "body_text": "There are two “Reduced Debug Info” options in the game, one is located in chat settings and one is a game rule called `reducedDebugInfo`. Make sure both are turned off (set to `false`).\\n\\n",
      "body_length": 189,
      "rendered_body": "<p>There are two “Reduced Debug Info” options in the game, one is located in chat settings and one is a game rule called <tt>reducedDebugInfo</tt>. Make sure both are turned off (set to <tt>false</tt>).</p>",
      "body": {
        "type": "doc",
        "version": 1,
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "There are two “Reduced Debug Info” options in the game, one is located in chat settings and one is a game rule called "
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "reducedDebugInfo",
                "marks": [
                  {
                    "type": "code"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": ". Make sure both are turned off (set to "
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "false",
                "marks": [
                  {
                    "type": "code"
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": ")."
              }
            ]
          }
